{"tid":947624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭紹傑及嚴敏華在日本提堂後繼續羈押","createTime":"2018-12-19T11:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T06:57:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":110,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8090b5af13d5cb3675317364cbc7efd5c010a4","tid":947624,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1434134_1_20181219192540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1434134_1_20181219192540.jpg&h=3e419147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保釣行動委員會成員郭紹傑及嚴敏華，日前在日本靖國神社外抗議後被捕。保釣行動委員會成員表示，案件今日在日本的法院提堂，由於法官需要時間考慮裁決，將案件押後，兩人需要繼續羈押。<br />\n<br />\n郭紹傑及嚴敏華本月12日，在日本靖國神社外抗議，郭紹傑展示抗議標語及叫口號，並焚燒甲級戰犯東條英機的仿製神主牌，嚴敏華則在旁拍攝，兩人其後被當地警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434134-20181219.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434134-20181219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=L1UbnfP%2BlHFpwzUq6hap85ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=21a28baf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434134-20181219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dd940b1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434134-20181219.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"38fa859af639dcc3af1109607c26e112150b6983","tid":947624,"uid":45772,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:50:11.000Z","msg":"判佢死刑啦屌！"},{"pid":"5d530ee16d70fcb6f44bc4d428f3eab8326fae51","tid":947624,"uid":48234,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:51:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">死刑! 死刑! 死刑!</span></span>"},{"pid":"9730348073d06f135f40b80ab227306cad80404e","tid":947624,"uid":997,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:55:30.000Z","msg":"直接拉去打靶啦"},{"pid